{
  "stem": "1338.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as a result, this camp was run by Russians, most of them Russian POWs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this particular guy was a German, but-- he spoke German very well, must have been a German Jew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know why, but he-- I think he had got a lot of influence, because he spoke German very well, and maybe got buddy-buddies with the management of the camp.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know the details.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I know that my head of my-- sorry-- my head of my barrack is-- was a musician, a German musician, don't know if a Jew or not.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I can't say.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Probably not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the head of the camp, despite the fact it was POWs, Russian POWs run mostly by Russian, the top man was a German.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I remember that one day I was-- you know, when you passed him, you had to take off your hat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I took my hat off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he walked up to me, and says, I'm a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You don't take a hat off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So he must have been some sort of a Social Democrat German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And, anyway, this guy managed to get me in the kitchen as a potato peeler.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I stayed most of the time there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I survived because of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Most of them were Russians, the potato peelers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And one of them was Serge Pipof.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Serge Pipof.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Young boy, 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He became my best friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took him after the war to the collection center for Russian refugees, which I blame myself for to this very day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I'll get to that back if we have enough tape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Til beginning of April, 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'45.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The head of it was a pilot, a Russian pilot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the head of the potato peelers.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
